}}{{TIDTOC|adapter}} ==Overview== [http://web.archive.org/web/20021027123119/http://www.bluetake.com/Products/BW009mini.htm Product page (via archive.org)] (first available page, dated October 27, 2002)
[http://web.archive.org/web/20050204062925/http://bluetake.com/Drivers/BTake_WLANb4.zip '''Bluetake''''s drivers for the device] indicate this device has a 03eb:7605 USB ID.. and thus uses AT76C503A.
Specifications, per '''Bluetake''''s product page, follow... *Power consumption **Tx: 330 mA max. **Rx: 220 mA max. *Tx Power: +18 dBm *Dimensions: [[Dimensions::78 mm x 67 mm x 20 mm]]
